<node CREATED="1614449539641" ID="ID_796625146" MODIFIED="1614449546433" TEXT="Generalization">
<node CREATED="1614533554600" ID="ID_694979298" MODIFIED="1614533913978">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      1. A generalization relationship is a parent-child relationship between use cases.
    </p>
    <p>
      2. The child use case is an enhancement of the parent use case.
    </p>
    <p>
      3. Generalization is shown as directed arrow with a triangle arrowhead.
    </p>
    <p>
      4. The child use case is connected at the base of the arrow. The tip of the arrow is connected to the parent use case.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
